ActExpungement of Historically Unjust Convictions Act
SubjectOrder Establishing Criteria Related to Certain Offences Listed in the Schedule to the Expungement of Historically Unjust Convictions Act
PrecisORDER ESTABLISHING CRITERIA RELATED TO CERTAIN OFFENCES LISTED IN THE SCHEDULE TO THE EXPUNGEMENT OF HISTORICALLY UNJUST CONVICTIONS ACT in order to establish criteria related to those offences to ensure that expungement can only be ordered for activities that are no longer criminal.
